# Pricing A/B Test Dashboard - Project Brief

## Project Overview
Interactive dashboard analyzing a two-period sequential pricing A/B test for dua.com (Albanian dating app) targeting male users across iOS/Android and Poor/Rich regions.

**Test Duration:** Jan 12 - Mar 19, 2026 (67 days total)
- **Period 1:** Jan 12-30 (19 days) - Initial pricing exploration
- **Period 2:** Jan 31-Mar 19 (48 days) - Refined pricing based on Period 1 winners

**Critical Data Cutoff:** March 19, 2026
- March 20-24 EXCLUDED due to Ramadan promotion contamination
- Original dataset went to Mar 24, but last clean data is Mar 19

---

## Test Structure

### Segments (4 total)
1. **Male | iOS | Poor Region** (Albania, Kosovo, North Macedonia, etc.)
   - Group A: 7,024 users | 737 converters | 10.49% CVR
   - Group B: 6,971 users | 836 converters | 11.99% CVR
   
2. **Male | iOS | Rich Region** (Germany, US, UK, Switzerland, etc.)
   - Group A: 3,939 users | 784 converters | 19.90% CVR
   - Group B: 3,915 users | 862 converters | 22.02% CVR

3. **Male | Android | Poor Region**
   - Group A: 2,454 users | 167 converters | 6.81% CVR
   - Group B: 2,467 users | 208 converters | 8.43% CVR

4. **Male | Android | Rich Region**
   - Group A: 906 users | 148 converters | 16.34% CVR
   - Group B: 995 users | 191 converters | 19.20% CVR

### Pricing Strategy
**Poor Region:**
- Period 1: Group A = P14-P36 (€6.99-€17.99), Group B = P5-P28 (€2.49-€13.99)
- Period 2: Group A = P5-P28, Group B = P12-P20 (€5.99-€9.99)
- Ages 18-24 ran as AA test (both groups P5-P10) in Period 2

**Rich Region:**
- Period 1: Group A = P24-P46 (€11.99-€22.99), Group B = P25-P47 (€12.49-€23.49)
- Period 2: Group A = P24-P46 (unchanged), Group B = P18-P40 (€8.99-€19.99)

